  ('SS-G4-EDM-ELO3', 'SS-G4-EDM', 'To understand how our natural resources play an important role in shaping our way of life: The Physical and Economic Benefits of Land Use', 313, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SS-G4-EDM-ELO4', 'SS-G4-EDM', 'To understand how our natural resources play an important role in shaping our way of life: The Blue Economy', 314, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SS-G4-EDM-ELO5', 'SS-G4-EDM', 'To understand how our natural resources play an important role in shaping our way of life: Our Coastal Environment and our Economy', 315, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SS-G4-EDM-ELO6', 'SS-G4-EDM', 'To understand how our natural resources play an important role in shaping our way of life: Renewable and Non-Renewable Energy', 316, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-RV-ELO1', 'LANG-G5-RV', 'Learners will select and engage with a wide range of paper-based, digital, and visual texts for independent reading, pleasure, and personal growth.', 316, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-LS-ELO1', 'LANG-G5-LS', ' The learner will explore, use, and critically apply oral language for pleasure, personal growth, to foster relationships and to develop an appreciation and celebration of culture and of oral languages. ', 317, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-RV-ELO2', 'LANG-G5-RV', 'Students will demonstrate a variety of ways to use background knowledge and interests to select and engage critically with a range of culturally diverse paper based, visual, and digital texts for pleasure and personal growth. ', 318, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-RV-ELO3', 'LANG-G5-RV', 'Students will interact with understanding and critical thought to a variety of genres and text forms using vocabulary, comprehension strategies and graphophonic cues.  ', 319, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-RV-ELO4', 'LANG-G5-RV', 'Students will develop their understanding of how an author’s choice of vocabulary, language, genre, text form, text features and style influence the meaning of text and define the author’s craft.  ', 320, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO1', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will generate, gather and organize ideas and information to write for a range of purposes and audiences, using the writing process independently and collaboratively.', 320, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO2', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will revise and edit written drafts to improve organization, style, and effectiveness for a variety of purposes and audiences.', 320, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO3', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will apply spelling conventions, grammar, and writing mechanics to enhance the precision and clarity of their written work.', 320, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO5', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will generate, gather, and organize thoughts to explore, clarify and reflect on thoughts, feelings, and experiences as they create a written or representative draft, independently and collaboratively, for a range of audiences and purposes. ', 321, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO6', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will revise the organization and language use in drafted writing or representation, collaboratively and independently, for a variety of purposes and audiences. ', 322, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('LANG-G5-WR-ELO7', 'LANG-G5-WR', 'Learners will use their knowledge of spoken language, written language and writing conventions to refine the precision and enhance the meaning and clarity of their written work. ', 323, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SPR-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G5-SPR', ' Develop a model to describe that matter is made of particles too small to be seen. ', 324, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SPR-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G5-SPR', ' Measure and graph quantities to provide evidence that regardless of the type of change that occurs when heating, cooling, or mixing substances, the total weight of matter is conserved. ', 325, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SPR-ELO3', 'SCIENCE-G5-SPR', 'Make observations and measurements to identify materials based on their properties. ', 326, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SPR-ELO4', 'SCIENCE-G5-SPR', 'Conduct an investigation to determine whether the mixing of two or more substances results in new substances.', 327, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ME-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G5-ME', ' Use models to describe that energy in animals’ food (used for body repair, growth, motion, and to maintain body warmth) was once energy from the sun. ', 328, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ME-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G5-ME', 'Support an argument that plants get the materials they need for growth chiefly from air and water. ', 329, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ME-ELO3', 'SCIENCE-G5-ME', ' Develop a model to describe the movement of matter among plants, animals, decomposers, and the environment.  ', 330, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ES-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G5-ES', ' Develop a model using an example to describe ways the geosphere, biosphere, hydrosphere, and/or atmosphere interact.  ', 331, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ES-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G5-ES', 'Describe and graph the amounts of salt water and fresh water in various reservoirs to provide evidence about the distribution of water on Earth.', 332, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-ES-ELO3', 'SCIENCE-G5-ES', 'Obtain and combine information about ways individual communities use science ideas to protect the Earth’s resources and environment.', 333, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SSS-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G5-SSS', 'Support an argument that the gravitational force exerted by Earth on objects is directed down.', 334, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SSS-ELO2', 'SCIENCE-G5-SSS', 'Support an argument that differences in the apparent brightness of the sun compared to other stars is due to their relative distances from Earth.', 335, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-SSS-ELO3', 'SCIENCE-G5-SSS', 'Represent data in graphical displays to reveal patterns of daily changes in length and direction of shadows, day and night, and the seasonal appearance of some stars in the night sky.', 336, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('SCIENCE-G5-EN-ELO1', 'SCIENCE-G5-EN', 'Plan and carry out fair tests in which variables are controlled and failure points are considered to identify aspects of a model or prototype that can be improved.', 337, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO1', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Whole Number – Saying Number Sequence, Meaningful Counting and Skip Counting', 338, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO2', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Whole Number – Representing and Partitioning Quantities', 339, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO3', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Whole Number – Comparing and Ordering Quantities', 340, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO4', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Whole Number – Understanding Place', 341, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO5', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Fractions, Decimals, and Rational Numbers– Representing Fractions', 342, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO6', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Fractions, Decimals and Rational Numbers – Comparing and Ordering Fractions', 343, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO7', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Fractions, Decimals and Rational Numbers – Representing Decimals', 344, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO8', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Fractions, Decimals and Rational Numbers – Comparing and Ordering Decimals', 345, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00'),
  ('MATH-G5-NS-ELO9', 'MATH-G5-NS', 'Fractions, Decimals and Rational Numbers – Decimal Place Value', 346, '2026-02-21T17:24:20.767466+00:00');
